description: Good Times Classic Ice Cream is a throw-back to the charming neighborhood ice cream trucks of our youth. A perfect addition to your next summertime birthday party, bar mitzvah, corporate function, charity, fund raiser or any private event.Our gorgeous 1966 International Harvester truck will take you back to a more simple time. We bring you a classic look, sounds and tastes experience that you will always remember and share with your friends and family. Truly a unique service.We specialize in bringing you the best in classic pre-packaged ice cream. We are also very happy to provide any special needs or requests.
name: Good Times Ice Cream
